Solution Approach:

Use MC 2.0 INT kubeconfig and connect to the cluster
Build the curl commands based on the input parameters to get access token
Get into the customer license pod using 'exec and /bin/bash'
execute the get access token curl command
get the token and build 'call to an api' curl command
execute the 'call to an api' curl command
Capture the results and show it in the console

